# SPA fallback for static hosts that honor _redirects (IPFS subdomain gateways
# incl. Pinata, Netlify, Cloudflare Pages). BrowserRouter uses real paths
# (/search, /entity/:id, /trip); without this, a direct load or refresh of those
# 404s. The CDN snapshot and hashed assets are real files and are served as-is —
# only unknown paths fall through to index.html (200, not a redirect).
/cdn/*  /cdn/:splat  200
/*      /index.html  200
